  "text": "Recognition based and recognition-recall. The second scheme i.e. recognition -recall CaRP is a new category which works by recognizing an image and using the recognized objects as cues to enter a password. Recognitionrecall combines the tasks of both recognition and cued recall. It retains the advantages of both schemes i.e. recognition advantage of being easy for human memory and the cuedrecall advantage of a large password space [CITATION_1] .",
